<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="perseverance-n">perseverance <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌpɜːsɪ'vɪərəns/    美 /ˌpɜːrsə'vɪrəns/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>锲而不舍；坚持不懈：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>persevered with</strong> her piano lessons.
她坚持不懈地学习钢琴。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>persevere in (doing) sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She persevered in her studies and graduated near the top of her class.
她坚持不懈地学习，以接近全班第一名的成绩毕业。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>perseverance /ˌpɜːsɪ'vɪərəns/ n   </p></div>